    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Silent Pathways</strong> is a first-person psychological horror game about uncovering the truth hidden in a family’s past. As Dave, you explore a decaying childhood home where reality twists with memory. Solve eerie environmental puzzles, piece together scattered diary entries and documents, and uncover forgotten lore that reveals what happened on that fateful day in 1965.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247620/extras/7ed3e1f66562feb8cf686182294d79f7.poster.avif?t=1758280506\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247620/extras/7ed3e1f66562feb8cf686182294d79f7.webm?t=1758280506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247620/extras/7ed3e1f66562feb8cf686182294d79f7.mp4?t=1758280506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every creak, every whisper, every shadow draws you deeper into the house’s secrets. But the more you discover, the more fragile your mind becomes - until you’re forced to face the horrors that refuse to be forgotten.</p>",
